{"word":"Zadok","slug":"zadok","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Zadok</b> <a href=\"#/H6659\">H6659</a> <br/> 1. High priest in time of David's reign:<br/> - General references<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=19&verse=11'>2Sa 19:11</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=20&verse=25'>2Sa 20:25</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=15&verse=11'>1Ch 15:11</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=16&verse=39'>1Ch 16:39</a> <br/> - Removes the ark from Jerusalem at the time of Absalom's usurpation; returns with it at David's command<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=15&verse=36'>2Sa 15:36</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=17&verse=15'>2Sa 17:15</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=17&verse=21'>2Sa 17:21</a> <br/> - Stands aloof from Adonijah at the time of his attempted usurpation<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=1&verse=8'>1Ki 1:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=1&verse=26'>1Ki 1:26</a> <br/> - Summoned by David to anoint Solomon<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=1&verse=40'>1Ki 1:40</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=1&verse=45'>1Ki 1:45</a> <br/> - Performs the function of high priest after Abiathar was deposed by Solomon<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=2&verse=35'>1Ki 2:35</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=29&verse=22'>1Ch 29:22</a> <br/> 2. Father of Jerusha<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=15&verse=33'>2Ki 15:33</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=27&verse=1'>2Ch 27:1</a><br/> 3. Son of Ahitub<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=6&verse=12'>1Ch 6:12</a><br/> 4. A man of valor<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=12&verse=28'>1Ch 12:28</a><br/> 5. Son of Baana<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=3&verse=4'>Neh 3:4</a><br/> 6. A priest<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=3&verse=29'>Neh 3:29</a><br/> 7. A returned exile<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=10&verse=21'>Neh 10:21</a><br/> 8. Son of Meraioth<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=11&verse=11'>Neh 11:11</a><br/> 9. A treasurer of the temple<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=13&verse=13'>Neh 13:13</a>"}]}